{"tid":1491082,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我要真普選！我要真普選！我要真普選！","createTime":"2019-08-20T09:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T14:46:32.000Z","uid":190579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd0c000ad7e3df7a9cf9eab708190f8f01caa6a","tid":1491082,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:45:22.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></ins><br />\n1. 撤回送中惡法<br />\n2. 成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n3. 撤回暴動定性<br />\n4. 釋放所有義士<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5. 我要真普選</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所有人認清政治現實，只要我地停止抗爭，中共就會慢慢清算我地。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人就會變成新彊人</span></strong></span><br />\n冇真普選，特首只係中央傀儡，林鄭2.0, 3.0，類似送中惡法只會不斷重覆<br />\n特區政府整個制度已經崩壞，不可修補。只有真普選先可以重建香港。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我要真普選</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我要真普選</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我要真普選</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"045c295d196d38af2954c8419285f3f885c12206","tid":1491082,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:45:30.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"36061f2f2098d160f038333e8198d5ad2c643861","tid":1491082,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"db0135da5015ec217ca5918ff57b6fd33a253b73","tid":1491082,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:46:10.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"7ce899bf5c3d92a1b43889df397735c556f44787","tid":1491082,"uid":226993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要傳出國際先有用。"},{"pid":"7a7596fc79cd2b5716d2a29560b2acf3be66bcd1","tid":1491082,"uid":87507,"like":0,"disl